Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.37,1:38:09.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a distant land this mountain high
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.21,1:38:18.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where all the music that we always kept inside will fill the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.08,1:38:26.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing in the silent swerve a heart is free
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.29,1:38:32.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While the world goes on turning and turning
